@AlloraNetwork combines AI and blockchain to build a more efficient and fair AI network.

1) Data Monopoly
few corporations dominate AI training data and models, making fair competition difficult.

2) Censorship and Bias
Centralized AI models can be influenced by specific agendas, leading to censorship or bias.

3) Lack of Reward Mechanisms

4) Unreliable Model Performance

Allora establish a new paradigm for operating AI in a more open and fair manner. 
The goal is to ensure that AI technology is not monopolized by specific corporations or institutions but is instead developed in a way that benefits all contributors. 
This will lead to a more transparent, trustworthy, and censorship resistant AI ecosystem.
